{"tid":1927102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為左光復香港你可以去到幾盡？","createTime":"2020-03-15T14:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T04:58:27.000Z","uid":117622,"like":107,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"608207abe5ca6278c17f2e1fc563eb7dfcb23a0b","tid":1927102,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXFHi0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXFHi0d.png&h=4554c896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依一班手足已經成為咗你哋嘅借鏡<br />\n<br />\n佢地成立工會已經<br />\n比左好多私人時間同金錢<br />\n為左香港出一份力<br />\n唔好諗你自己唔得<br />\n唔好諗做唔做得黎<br />\n我話俾你聽<span style=\"color: red;\">你一定得</span><br />\n點解我咁肯定因為我就係上面嗰班人其中一個<br />\n只要你肯大把人幫你<br />\n<br />\n睇到個post嘅手足<br />\n要認真諗諗而家嘅你<br />\n究竟你仲可唔可以行多一步<br />\n成立工會<br />\n進攻功能組別<br />\n光復立法會<br />\n切切實實實現五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com/?fbclid=IwAR1OMXpZ4bXNY1lHNNFwDylDj74Pj00qj3IaEYFK2Adddjkj5PvXwCPLWtM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1OMXpZ4bXNY1lHNNFwDylDj74Pj00qj3IaEYFK2Adddjkj5PvXwCPLWtM&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=e6ea3bfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com/?fbclid=IwAR1OMXpZ4bXNY1lHNNFwDylDj74Pj00qj3IaEYFK2Adddjkj5PvXwCPLWtM</a><br />\n「七起」網站<br />\n搵夠七個人成立工會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進攻功能組別冇用？<br />\n唔試過點知冇用<br />\n無論你選擇用邊個方法都好<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n光復香港"},{"pid":"9c4256004f59242d0f69665c01331e44bcacf6ad","tid":1927102,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404a81ee63af3a88b4b6f2ef72689f9787b53ac1","tid":1927102,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:39:24.000Z","msg":"學生哥但幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e8ada7b9ea12415720c9846f91c9e6c016eb6a","tid":19