br />\n唔好諗你自己唔得<br />\n唔好諗做唔做得黎<br />\n我話俾你聽<span style=\"color: red;\">你一定得</span><br />\n點解我咁肯定因為我就係上面嗰班人其中一個<br />\n只要你肯大把人幫你<br />\n<br />\n睇到個post嘅手足<br />\n要認真諗諗而家嘅你<br />\n究竟你仲可唔可以行多一步<br />\n成立工會<br />\n進攻功能組別<br />\n光復立法會<br />\n切切實實實現五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com/?fbclid=IwAR1OMXpZ4bXNY1lHNNFwDylDj74Pj00qj3IaEYFK2Adddjkj5PvXwCPLWtM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1OMXpZ4bXNY1lHNNFwDylDj74Pj00qj3IaEYFK2Adddjkj5PvXwCPLWtM&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=e6ea3bfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com/?fbclid=IwAR1OMXpZ4bXNY1lHNNFwDylDj74Pj00qj3IaEYFK2Adddjkj5PvXwCPLWtM</a><br />\n「七起」網站<br />\n搵夠七個人成立工會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進攻功能組別冇用？<br />\n唔試過點知冇用<br />\n無論你選擇用邊個方法都好<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n光復香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T22:50:35.000Z","msg":"小知識:黃色工會有其他意思<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/黄色工会\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%E5%B7%A5%E4%BC%9A&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=ef2340e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/黄色工会</a><br />\n所以唔好亂用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然大家都明&rdquo;黃色&rdquo;工會係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a1deeda459d80ff67ed5d3e0a9a9d8a026e8ed","tid":1927102,"uid":80653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T22:52:16.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"c4d32af7748024e849961f407202f17fc0df24f5","tid":1927102,"uid":49196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ccf9b5a15fd15c979dad607c374e92c7c3ce5c0","tid":1927102,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"工聯會地址???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T22:53:04.000Z","msg":"乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 